premise_source_doc_sentence: LaMelo Ball  (  born August 22 , 2001  )  is an American basketball player who attends Chino Hills High School in Chino Hills , California .
A sophomore point guard for his high school team , he has repeatedly drawn attention from national media .
In his first season at Chino Hills , Ball won the California state championship with his brothers Lonzo and LiAngelo .
He was considered one of the top freshmen in the country .
Ball verbally committed to play college basketball for UCLA when he was 13 years old .
